### Games and Guesses API Testing

### Get all games
GET http://localhost:8000/games
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get a specific game by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/games/1
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get games for a specific user
GET http://localhost:8000/games?user_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Create a new game for user 1
POST http://localhost:8000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "word_to_guess": "PLANT",
    "status": "in_progress"
}

###
### Create a new game for user 2
POST http://localhost:8000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 2,
    "word_to_guess": "BEACH",
    "status": "in_progress"
}

###
### Get all guesses
GET http://localhost:8000/guesses
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Get guesses for a specific game
GET http://localhost:8000/guesses?game_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###
### Add a guess to a game
POST http://localhost:8000/guesses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "game_id": 1,
    "attempt_no": 3,
    "guess_word": "PLANT",
    "feedback": "GR,GR,GR,GR,GR"
}

###
### Add another guess (attempt 3 for game 2)
POST http://localhost:8000/guesses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "game_id": 2,
    "attempt_no": 3,
    "guess_word": "TRACK",
    "feedback": "GR,GR,GR,GR,GR"
}
